<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/main_style.css" type="text/css" />
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>BuildRunMate</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="__next">
    <div>
      <div style="min-height: calc(100vh - 215px); padding-bottom: 40px">
        <nav
          class="z-50 hidden h-20 select-none items-center border-b px-6 text-base md:flex"
        >
          <a
            class="flex items-center space-x-2 hover:opacity-70"
            href="/<%= id %>"
          >
            <div class="h-full font-logo text-2xl font-bold text-swygBlue-500">
              BuildRunMate
            </div>
          </a>
          <ul class="ml-4 flex h-full items-center font-medium">
            <li class="group flex h-full items-center">
              <a
                target=""
                class="mt-1 py-2 px-6 group-hover:text-gray-900"
                href="/<%= id %>/enroll"
                >프로젝트 등록</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="group flex h-full items-center">
              <a
                target=""
                class="mt-1 py-2 px-6 group-hover:text-gray-900"
                href="/<%= id %>/find_projects"
                >프로젝트 찾기</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-1 flex flex-1 items-center justify-end space-x-6">
            <h1 style="font-size: 17px">Welcome, <%= id %></h1>
          </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="relative py-24 md:py-10">
          <section
            class="relative mx-auto flex w-full max-w-7xl flex-col-reverse justify-between md:flex-row"
          >
            <div
              class="z-10 flex-1 py-10 text-center md:py-32 md:pl-6 md:text-left"
            >
              <h1
                class="font-logo text-xl font-bold text-swygBlue-500 sm:text-2xl"
              >
                Find Your Project Mate
              </h1>
              <div class="mt-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 sm:space-y-10">
                  <h2
                    class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-2 text-2xl font-bold sm:text-4xl md:justify-start md:space-x-0 md:space-y-4 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
                  >
                    <span>당신의 프로젝트메이트를</span>
                    <span>찾아보세요.</span>
                  </h2>
                  <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
                    함께할 메이트를 구한다면 누구나
                  </h3>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center space-x-4 md:justify-start">
                <a
                  class="btn-container btn-animation bg-swygBlue-500 font-bold text-gray-100"
                  href="/<%= id %>/enroll"
                  >프로젝트 등록</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
